vote.title: An ordinance abandoning portions of two temporary working space easements to IDIL Prairie Creek, LLC, the abutting owner, containing a total of approximately 62,345 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Military Parkway and Prairie Creek Road; and providing for the dedication of a total of approximately 19,244 square feet of land needed for a sanitary sewer easement - Revenue: General Fund $5,400.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
